Resonance Filter: Only configurations that satisfy coherence thresholds (BRST nilpotency, SPD integrity, Valence balance) survive into stable shards.

Emergence Trigger: When local curvature, Valence, and memory metrics align, the RCZ â€œsnaps inâ€ a shard â€” a lawful lift from potential into stable Dâ‚ƒ matter.

Thermodynamic Buffer: The RCZ is where entropy is lawfully managed: Î”S is minimized by balancing coherence inflow (photons) with containment pressure (leptons).

